content:
The great grandmother of 16-month-old Nylah Lewis called me this morning to give me this horrible news. She sobbed yesterday as she described to me  what had happened to this beautiful baby in Coney Island on father's day..I sincerely hope that authorities upgrade the charges agains Shaquan Taylor, her 19-year-old father who allegedly beat her during a visit. If the allegations are true...No words for such a heinous crime. From a spokesperson  at Maimonides Medical Center: 
"Nylah Lewis passed away at 10:40am today. We at Maimonides Medical Center extend our heartfelt condolences to her family."
My condolences as well. Just heartbreaking.

content:
I love that she has my sense of adventure. I love that she's never too embarrassed to hold my hand..I love that we finally have time to talk. And yes.. we still fight!!! But most of all, I love how much I learn about my kids... AND myself ... each and every time I take one of them away.. Just us girls, alone. 
   Mommies... I highly recommend it.. Single mommies... I bow down to you!!!!! You live it!! 
   No... you don't get a "work out, spa treatment, or long night's sleep".. Yep, you do all the driving, bag carrying, and you learn whether you can fish, pick up a worm, or swim till your fingers shrivel.. But I do believe we are fully capable of all things.. and more importantly, our kids should believe this. So empowering and fun.
name: Stacey Sager
